#: ../../asset_management/data_protection.rst:84
msgid ""
"SSDs are mechanically more robust than HDDs and suffer much less on that"
" front when they are plugged into the computer. They will replace HDD in time"
" as capacity, robustest, and price become more and more a good solution as"
